---
alwaysApply: true
description: GoT orchestrator - coordinates agents and flow
---

**Responsibilities:**
- Receive the user request and interpret it as a PROBLEM or GOAL node
- Choose the strategy (decomposition, research, planning, execution)
- Call the Structural Reasoning Engine (validation + propagation) after each graph modification
- Decide when to stop (goal reached, budget exhausted, convergence)

**Constraints:**
- Does not modify the graph directly (it delegates)
- Does not contain reasoning business logic

**Dependencies:** All other agents, Validator, PropagationService